OL,3,CThe Miners' Strike: Communities
OL,4,Creflect on year that 'changed Wales
OL,5,Cforever'
OL,7,F40 years ago, thousands of colliers in
OL,8,FWales downed tools and rose up. The
OL,9,FMiners' Strike spanned twelve bitter,
OL,10,Fbrutal months.
OL,12,FAt the heart of the dispute was a
OL,13,Ffight to stop pit closures and save
OL,14,Fjobs.
OL,16,FIn a special ITV Wales programme
OL,17,FStories from the Strike, men and women
OL,18,Ffrom across Wales reflect on the
OL,19,Fconflict that changed their lives
OL,20,Fforever.
