OL,3,CThe Miners' Strike: Communities
OL,4,Creflect on year that 'changed Wales
OL,5,Cforever'
OL,7,FPaul Davies worked in Blaenant
OL,8,FColliery, and became an active
OL,9,Fpicketer during the strike.
OL,11,FHe was one of many men arrested after
OL,12,Fhe climbed a crane in Port Talbot to
OL,13,Fprevent coal leaving the dock.
OL,15,F"We had no choice but to fight at that
OL,16,Ftime," he said. "We tried our best to
OL,17,Fsave our jobs. We failed.
