OL,3,CThe Miners' Strike: Communities
OL,4,Creflect on year that 'changed Wales
OL,5,Cforever'
OL,7,F"At the time, as a married man, I
OL,8,Fdidn't realise what the implications
OL,9,Fwere, I don't think my friends did
OL,10,Feither.
OL,12,F"We certainly didn't think it would
OL,13,Flast a year.
OL,15,F"Come the May, when Danielle was born,
OL,16,Fit was a case of 'how do we provide
OL,17,Fsomething when we have nothing?'
