OL,3,CThe Miners' Strike: Communities
OL,4,Creflect on year that 'changed Wales
OL,5,Cforever'
OL,7,F"It used to knot my stomach going in
OL,8,Feach day. Lads were calling me a scab,
OL,9,Fwhich I will be for the rest of my
OL,10,Fdays.
OL,12,F"Until my last breath I will be a
OL,13,Fscab. There's still that feeling now
OL,14,Fin this community."
OL,16,FJayne Headon-Francis is the daughter
OL,17,Fof Hefina Headon, the activist who was
OL,18,Fimmortalised by Imelda Staunton in the
OL,19,Ffilm PRIDE.
